/> in den Warenkorb</a></div>\r\n  		<div class=\\\"trenner\\\"><img src=\\\"\".$REX[HTDOCS_PATH].\"files/linie.gif\\\"  border=0 width=445 /></div>\";\r\n\r\n\r\n	}\r\n}\r\necho $output;\r\necho \"\";\r\n\r\n\r\n?>','','<?php\r\nfunction add_cat_options( &$select, &$cat, &$cat_ids, $groupName = \'\') {\r\n    if( empty( $cat)) {\r\n        return;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    $cat_ids[] = $cat->getId();\r\n    $select->add_option($cat->getName(),$cat->getId(), $groupName);\r\n    $childs = $cat->getChildren();\r\n\r\n    if ( is_array( $childs)) {\r\n        foreach ( $childs as $child) {\r\n            add_cat_options( $select, $child, $cat_ids, $cat->getName());\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\n$selected = \"REX_VALUE[1]\";\r\nif($selected == \"\"){\r\n	$selected = \"REX_ARTICLE_ID\";\r\n}\r\n\r\n$sel_cat = new select;\r\n$sel_cat->set_style(\"width:100%;\");\r\n$sel_cat->set_size(1);\r\n$sel_cat->set_name(\"VALUE[1]\");\r\n$sel_cat->set_selected($selected);\r\n$STYLE= \"onchange=\'document.forms.catsearch.submit();\'\";\r\n$sel_cat->add_option(\"Bitte eine Kategorie auswählen\",\"100000000000000000\");\r\n\r\n$cat_ids = array();\r\nif ($rootCats = OOCategory::getRootCategories())\r\n{\r\n	foreach( $rootCats as $rootCat) {\r\n	    add_cat_options( $sel_cat, $rootCat, $cat_ids);\r\n	}\r\n}\r\n\r\necho \"Bitte eine Produktkategorie auswählen:<br />\";\r\necho $sel_cat->out().\"<br /><br />\";\r\n\r\n\r\necho \"Bitte Sortierung festlegen:<br />\";\r\n$sel = new select;\r\n$sel->set_style(\"width:100%;\");\r\n$sel->set_size(1);\r\n$sel->set_name(\"VALUE[2]\");\r\n$sel->add_option(\"Nach Titel/Name\",\"name asc\");\r\n$sel->add_option(\"Nach Preis\",\"price asc\");\r\n$sel->set_selected(\"REX_VALUE[2]\");\r\necho $sel->out();\r\n\r\n?>','','0','0','','','','0','0');
